title: Spectator server data request failed lol replay
body:
Hello evrybody!
Today i m trying dowland replay Rules game,  when i m launched replay, he didnt started. Only black screen, agter i m get eror:Spectator server data request failed. The game will now exit.
Help me pls 
(And sorry for my perfecto English)

replies.body: Was the game you're trying to watch played on this patch, or was it possibly played before this patch came out? If it was from a prior patch, it won't be playable anymore unless you already made a highlight. If it was played on this current patch though, you might be able to get things working normally again with a quick repair.
I'm trying watched game on this patch. Okay i ll try quick repair. But what i should do if this didn't work?
